1615 // calculate act_surface_runoff
1616 // used for manure, scattered settlements, industrial fertilizer, open defecation, geogenic background
1617 double (*act_surface_runoff)[12] = NULL; //WaterGAP surface runoff consists of all runoff: from land and urban areas
1618 double *act_surface_runoff_year = NULL;
1619 double *act_surface_runoff_summer= NULL;
1620
1621 if (toCalc==0||toCalc==1||toCalc==2||toCalc==3||toCalc==4) { // for BOD, TDS, FC, TN and TP
1622 act_surface_runoff = new double[continent.ng][12]; //WaterGAP surface runoff consists of all runoff: from land and urban areas
1623 act_surface_runoff_year = new double[continent.ng];
1624 act_surface_runoff_summer= new double[continent.ng];
1625
1626 for (int cell=0; cell<continent.ng; cell++) {
1627 act_surface_runoff_year[cell] =0.0;
1628 act_surface_runoff_summer[cell]=0.0;
1629 //if(cell==58694)
1630 //cout<<"sur_runoff_cell[cell][0]: "<<sur_runoff_cell[cell][0]<<" urban_runoff_cell[cell][0]: "<<urban_runoff_cell[cell][0]<<endl;
1631
1632 for(int month=0; month<12; month++) {
1633 if (sur_runoff_cell[cell][month]==NODATA|| urban_runoff_cell[cell][month]==NODATA) act_surface_runoff[cell][month]=NODATA;
1634 else {
1635 if (sur_runoff_cell[cell][month]>=0.0 && urban_runoff_cell[cell][month]>=0.0){
1636 act_surface_runoff[cell][month]=sur_runoff_cell[cell][month]-urban_runoff_cell[cell][month];
1637 if(act_surface_runoff[cell][month]<0)
1638 act_surface_runoff[cell][month]=0; //may happen because of the way WaterGAP calculates. This will be changed in WaterGAP soon
1639 act_surface_runoff_year[cell]+= act_surface_runoff[cell][month];
1640 if((month>1) && (month <10))
1641 act_surface_runoff_summer[cell]+=act_surface_runoff[cell][month];
1642 }else{
1643 act_surface_runoff[cell][month]=NODATA;
1644 act_surface_runoff_year[cell]=NODATA;
1645 }
1646 }
1647 } // for(month)
1648
1649 } //for(cell)
1650 }

3718 if (sur_runoff_cell[cell][month]==NODATA && gw_runoff_cell[cell][month]==NODATA)
3719 runoff_cell = NODATA;
3720 else {
3721 if (sur_runoff_cell[cell][month]!=NODATA ) runoff_cell += sur_runoff_cell[cell][month];
3722 if (gw_runoff_cell[cell][month]!=NODATA ) runoff_cell += gw_runoff_cell[cell][month];
3723 }

3730 ld_background_cell_year[cell]+=ld_background_cell[cell][month];

3735 ld_background_cell_year[cell]+=ld_background_cell[cell][month];
3736 } else {
3737 ld_background_cell[cell][month] = NODATA;
3738 }

3740 ld_background_cell[cell][month] = NODATA;

3834 ld_agr_cell_year[cell] = NODATA;
3835 }

3837
3838
3839
3840 } // for(cell)
3841 }

4100void ClassWQ_load::calc_ld_agr_cell(int cell, int month, double ld_agr_soil_lastMonth, double ld_agr_lastMonth) {
4101 if (cell < 0 || cell >= continent.ng) {
4102 cerr << "cell "<< cell << " not exist!!! error in calc_ld_agr_cell.\n"; return;
4103 }
4104 if (month < 0 || month >= 12) {
4105 cerr << "month "<< month+1 << " not exist!!! error in calc_ld_agr_cell.\n"; return;
4106 }
4107
4108 if (organic_carbon[cell] == NODATA) {
4109 ld_agr_soil_cell[cell][month] = NODATA;
4110 ld_agr_cell[cell][month] = NODATA;
4111 } else {
4112 double f1 = 1.;
4113// if (g_slope[cell]<0.2) {
4114// f1 = 0.001423 * pow(g_slope[cell]*100.,2.) + 0.02153 * g_slope[cell]*100.;
4115// }
4116
4117 if (g_land_slope[cell]<20.) {
4118 f1 = 0.001423 * pow(g_land_slope[cell],2.) + 0.02153 * g_land_slope[cell];
4119 }
4120 double f2 = pow(0.83, WBZ_cell[cell]);
4121 double f = f1 * f2;
4122
4123 double Kd = koc * organic_carbon[cell]/100.;
4124
4125 double Dt = 1.; // Einheit gleich mit DT50soil: Monat
4126 double exponent = exp(-Dt * log(2.)/DT50soil);
4127 ld_agr_soil_cell[cell][month] = ld_input_pest[cell] + ld_agr_soil_lastMonth * exponent - ld_agr_lastMonth;
4128 ld_agr_cell[cell][month] = 0;
4129 if (precipitation_cell[cell][month]>0.) {
4130 ld_agr_cell[cell][month] = ld_agr_soil_cell[cell][month] *
4131 sur_runoff_cell[cell][month] / precipitation_cell[cell][month] * f /(1+Kd);
4132 }
4133
4134 if (cell==0 || cell==79140 || cell==80363 || cell==110551)
4135 {
4136 cout << cell+1 << '\t' << month+1 << '\t' << g_land_slope[cell]
4137 << '\t' << f1 << '\t' << f2 << '\t' << f << '\t' << koc
4138 << '\t' << organic_carbon[cell]<< '\t' <<Kd << '\t' << exponent
4139 << '\t' << DT50soil<< '\t' << sur_runoff_cell[cell][month]
4140 << '\t' << precipitation_cell[cell][month]<< '\t' << ld_agr_cell[cell][month]
4141 << '\t' << ld_input_pest[cell] << '\t' << ld_agr_soil_cell[cell][month] << '\t'
4142 << ld_agr_soil_lastMonth << '\t' << ld_agr_lastMonth
4143 << endl;
4144 }
4145 } // nicht NODATA
4146
4147} // calc_ld_agr_cell
